      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA ULTIMATE (1) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and one placing from three starts. Below best last time at Ballarat (22.74) in a Grade 5, finishing a 8 length sixth. Rates on top and should go close. HIGH END CASH (3) could manage only eighth at this track last time but turned heads when clocking a dazzling 16.41 over 300m at this track three starts back. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. KNEE DEEP (8) is a well performed dog and winner of 23 races who was in the minor money last time out at this track (16.66). Form here at the trip sound including 13 wins. Hard to beat again. ESPECIAL KAI (7) is a last start winner worth following up.",
